data.title: Isaac Ross - 2024 - Football
data.meta_description: Isaac Ross (14) QB  - PERSONAL: Isaac Ross was born January 14, 2004...the son of Justin & Trisha Ross...four-year letterwinner and three-year starter for Head Coach
data.text:
PERSONAL: Isaac Ross was born January 14, 2004...the son of Justin & Trisha Ross...four-year letterwinner and three-year starter for Head Coach Gary Heide at Bayfield High School...threw for over 3,300 yards with over 2,000 coming in one season...Second Team All-State and two-time All-Conference honoree...also member of baseball & basketball teams.

MAJOR: Exercise Science

Freshman Season (2022):

Appeared in one game as a freshman.

Sophomore Season (2023):

Appeared in three games for the Quakers…Went 2-3 passing for 35 yards, with a long pass of 31 yards…Ran the ball four times for 25 yards, with a long rush of 15 yards.
